comments.content: [Gelato Script](http://web.archive.org/web/20140823162901/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/schizotype/gelato-script/) (using some of the alternate swash glyphs).

By the way, you've posted this font ID request in the "General Discussion" forum -- Which is identified on the page where you select forums, as follows:

**All topics are welcome—except font ID requests**.

For font identification you go to
